{"tid":637781,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山神發短訊感謝雲加","createTime":"2018-04-22T06:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T11:08:55.000Z","uid":46892,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdfd8076232ef6acea4c6a2300a80deec25230b","tid":637781,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0HwJE49gAfonorBSzpbb2f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1414e5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿歷斯山齊士與雲加有沒有前者轉會而影響感情？不知道，只知山神得悉雲加季尾將離隊後，不忘送上祝福。<br />\n<br />\n阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）在曼聯周末足總盃4強戰打敗熱刺後，少不免被問到前效球會主帥雲加即將離隊的看法。他承認向前帥雲加予以祝福。他說：「我在昨日發短訊給他，祝福他。我不能在社交網絡說甚麼，但我發短訊予他，而他回覆我，說多謝我。」<br />\n<br />\n「這令人傷心，因為他具歷史性的足球傳奇，我時常說他是一名紳士，也是足球大師，他在尊重人及要專業方面教曉我很多。我就是很感激他。」<br />\n<br />\n山齊士早前透露在他加盟曼聯前，雲加曾經挽留他，更指他是兵工廠陣中的最佳球員，只是山神決心追夢，雲加才無奈接受他的離隊決定。"},{"pid":"563d1657e51a962c7a7c49a0f45e0de0b44e524a","tid":637781,"uid":33601,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:54:50.000Z","msg":"追夢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d5d2be16612e8a37c3efce21283cc58749b1e0","tid":637781,"uid":3244,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7f57feab123ae9e95bda9b4f94da58d50a82fa8","tid":637781,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"6bfcbae7267cc9f3526d703fb354e569dbf26de7","tid":637781,"uid":36497,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"算你啦仆街仔"},{"pid":"f129fbdfad0752651a7cd0ef45e9d2e5d9a23cda","tid":637781,"uid":11055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T07: